om/books?id=JKMNuwMAmr4C&pg=PT341&dq=coined+thermodynamics&lr=&ei=z2HJSPDtHYzQjgGg2sCKDA&sig=ACfU3U3ig6THoGxAmK4zgqeCQ_PUl0L1Yg" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><font color="#800080">pg. 331</font></a><font color="#000000">). Informa Health Care.</font> </blockquote>12. Rankine, William. (1855). &ldquo;<a class="external" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=dzxVAAAAMAAJ&printsec=titlepage#PRA1-PA209,M1" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><font color="#0000ff">Outlines of the Science of Energetics</font></a>&rdquo;, <i>Read before the Philosophical Society of Glasgow </i>on May 2, and published in the <i>Proceedings</i> of that Society, Vol. III., No. VI.   <br>13. <font color="#000000">Prisyazhniuk, Vitaly. (2007). &ldquo;</font><a class="external" href="http://www.eoearth.org/article/History_of_thermodynamics" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><font color="#800080">History of thermodynamics</font></a><font color="#000000">&rdquo;, <i>Encyclopedia of Earth.</i></font><br>14. <font color="#333333">Tait, Peter G. (1868). <i><a class="external" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=XRwAAAAAQAAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=Sketch+of+Thermodynamics" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Sketch of Thermodynamics</a></i>.  Edmonston and Douglas.</font><br><br><div align="center"><div align="center">  <div align="center"><div align="center">  <div align="center"><a href="/page/%CE%B8%E2%88%86ics" target="_self"><img align="bottom" alt="TDics icon ns" height="31" src="http://image.wikifoundry.com/image/1/_zpkwDViWzKHeh3XrOqk3Q8688/GW69H31" title="TDics icon ns" width="69"></a></div></div></div></div></div><br> contentType 9 text/html url 59 https://www.eoht.info:443/page/Thermodynamics%20(etymology) responseCode 3 200 